p
\left(\frac{2}{p}\right)=\left(\frac{8-p}{p}\right)=\left(\frac{p}{p-8}\right)=\left(\frac{8}{p-8}\right)=\left(\frac{2}{p-8}\right) 
8-p\equiv8\pmod p
\left({8-p\over p}\right)=\left({8\over p}\right)=\left({2\over p}\right)\left({4\over p}\right)=\left({2\over p}\right)
